\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathrm{conv}=\mathrm{abs}\left(\mathbf{\Phi}_{S,i}-\mathbf{\Phi}_{S,i-1}\right)
\]

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $i\mbox{ }$
\end_inset

